title: NFL Trade Deadline Recap, Fantasy Football Implications
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jason La Canfora and Dave Richard to break down the 2018 NFL trade deadline, examining whether the Broncos moving Demaryius Thomas was smart and if the Eagles win big by landing Golden Tate, as well as looking at the Dante Fowler trade to the Rams and the Ha-Ha Clinton-Dix trade to the Redskins.
